These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Beverage:7up is in the numerically lowest position or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Nationality: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Nationality:french is on the left of Nationality:nigerian##1
3. Nationality:nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:french == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Nationality:german is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
6. Nationality:french == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
Music-Genre: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. Hobby:drawing is between Music-Genre:blues and Music-Genre:reggae##2
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Hobby:cooking##1
3. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:folk is on the left of Music-Genre:reggae##1
5. Music-Genre:folk is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

