.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
Nationality: american, australian, indian, russian
1. Music-Genre:jazz is on the right of Nationality:russian##1
2. Nationality:australian == Music-Genre:punk##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Music-Genre:folk##1
4. Music-Genre:hip-hop is in the numerically lowest position##1
5. Music-Genre:jazz is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is in the numerically lowest position or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

