.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
Movie-Genre: epic, family, mystery, western
Transport: car, quad-bike, roller, ship
1. Transport:ship is in an odd position##4
2. Transport:roller is on the left of Transport:car##1
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Movie-Genre:mystery##1
4. Transport:ship == Movie-Genre:epic##1
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Transport:car##3
6. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Transport:car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

