2. Job:teacher is in an odd position##4
3. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left or right of Job:teacher##3
4. Job:teacher is on the right of Pet:guinea-pig##1
5. Job:coach is between Job:teacher and Job:pilot##2
6. Pet:fish is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:fish is between Job:coach and Pet:goat##2
8. Job:coach is on the left or right of Job:pilot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | pilot | coach      | teacher | project-manager |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

