.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
Music-Genre: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. Beverage:almond-milk == Music-Genre:jazz##1
2. Music-Genre:disco is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:disco and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:jazz is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Music-Genre:dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

