1. Hobby:board-games is between Sport:ice-hockey and Hobby:chess##2
2. Hobby:magic-tricks is in the numerically lowest position or far right##3
3. Hobby:chess is on the left of Sport:weightlifting##1
4. Hobby:skydiving is on the left of Hobby:chess##1
5. Sport:weightlifting is in an odd position##4
