.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: 7up, fanta, milk, water
Food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. Food:kale is in the numerically lowest position##1
2. Beverage:milk is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
3. Beverage:water is in the numerically lowest position or far right##3
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
6. Food:pepper is in an even position##4
7. Food:corn == Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

