3. Transport:jet-ski is between Job:entrepreneur and Transport:helicopter##2
4. Job:manager is in the numerically lowest position or far right##3
5. Transport:subway is on the right of Job:software-developer##1
6. Transport:subway is in the numericaly highest position##1

